title.narrative: Building institutional capacities for the sustainable management of the marine fishery in the Red Sea State (Phase II)

description.narrative: By continuing to strengthen institutional capacities of the Marine Fisheries Administration for the development and maintenance of a Fishery Statistics System and the development, implementation and monitoring of Ecosystem Based Management plans for two key commercial species, the project will further consolidate the knowledge base for the sustainable management and development of artisanal and semi-industrial fisheries in the Red Sea Sate of the Republic of Sudan.
